Title: Que Será Será
Plot: The team encounters logistical problems while trying to run tests on a 600-pound man due to his extremely large size. Meanwhile, House spends the night in jail after being arrested by Detective Tritter for various charges, including resisting arrest.
GuestStars: Mary Elizabeth Ellis, Kadeem Hardison, Stephanie Venditto, Pruitt Taylor Vince, Alan Frazier, Michael James Faradie, Ryan Brockington, Bruno Amato, Richard Chance, Denver Dowridge, Jim Vickers, Damien Wayans, Co
